# Keep the Docker build context (the repo root, COPY . /DiFfRG) small: exclude
# build trees, caches, VCS metadata and other host-only artifacts. Anything the
# in-container CMake build needs (dependencies/, DiFfRG/, patches/, CMakeLists)
# is fetched fresh or lives in the tracked tree.
build/
bin/
**/bin/
**/build/
.git/
.venv/
.cache/
.idea/
.devcontainer/
containers/logs/
thoughts/
.claude/
slurm-*.out
*.log
**/*.o
**/*.a
**/__pycache__/
